results.name: Irregular triangle read by rows in which row n lists the emergent parts of all partitions of n, or 0 if such parts do not exist.
comment: For the definition of "emergent part" see A182699 and also A182709.
Also [0, 0, 0, 0] followed by the positive integers of the rows that contain zeros in the triangle A193870. For another version see A193827. - Omar E. Pol, Aug 12 2011
xref: Row n has length A182699(n). Row sums give A182709.
results.author: _Omar E. Pol_, Aug 07 2011
